---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy — GitOrbit">
  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-text-secondary">Last updated: April 8, 2026</p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Overview</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary">
        GitOrbit is a zero-backend static web application. We do not collect, store, or process any personal information. 
        All authentication happens through your GitHub Personal Access Token (PAT), which is stored exclusively in your 
        browser's localStorage and is never transmitted to any server other than GitHub's API.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Data We Don't Collect</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-text-secondary">
        <li>No personal information</li>
        <li>No usage analytics</li>
        <li>No error tracking or crash reporting</li>
        <li>No cookies or tracking pixels</li>
        <li>No server-side logs (there is no server)</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Token Storage</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary">
        Your GitHub PAT is stored in your browser's localStorage and is only sent to api.github.com and 
        raw.githubusercontent.com when making authenticated requests to the GitHub API. The token is never 
        logged, sent to third parties, or stored anywhere else.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">State Data</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary">
        All application state (repositories, runs, prompts) is stored in a dedicated GitHub repository that you control. 
        This data is subject to GitHub's privacy policy and terms of service.
      </p>
      
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary">
        For privacy-related questions, please contact us at{' '}
        <a href="mailto:whyiswhen@gmail.com" class="text-accent-light hover:underline">
          whyiswhen@gmail.com
        </a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
